<h3 id="_linking_payment_terminals">5.2. Linking payment terminals</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Some card terminals can be linked to plentymarkets POS by provisioning plugins in the plentymarkets back end. plentymarkets POS currently support the following card terminals:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/en/plugins/payment/ingenicozvt_5140" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ingenico devices via ZVT interface</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/en/plugins/payment/sumup_5141" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SumUp Air</a></p>
</li>
